title: Bushcraft Build-Off
overview: Hosted by primitive skills master Matt Graham, Bushcraft Build-Off is an all-new competition series where elite builders compete in a grueling, seven-day race against the clock. This competition will test the primitive building skills that have allowed survivalists to thrive in the wilderness for generations. But is now amplified on the web and through social media as these young masters attempt to outdo one another with more and more elaborate builds.
